&lt;p&gt;Created technical content that&#39;s driven measurable impact on adoption or understanding&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skills with data visualization and interactive web technologies that enhance storytelling&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A portfolio of projects that demonstrate both technical depth and narrative thinking&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
